snippet.title: Crackin’ Cases
snippet.description:
This channel is dedicated to looking in and researching cases of missing children, true crime, etc. Crackin’ Cases is a husband and wife duo (Cam and Alli) who tries to look at each case with a wide open visual approach, not following the main stream agenda and the tunnel vision used by many others. Always focusing on victims and their families to give support and help them receive justice for the crimes against them. Our main statement is this: At the end of the day, everybody wants to see justice, but justice doesn’t have to be carried out with hate!

Join the channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCvAJvAKn-KcFQMk_VWCD2GQ/join
